Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm working with my girlfriend, Rie, at the same company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we're in different offices,\Nso we hardly see each other during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been going out for about two years, from when I was at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since she was eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems so easy to get tired of seeing the same person after two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she's very attractive, and I'm still attracted to her,\Nso I don't even want to cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess it must mean I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The story how we met is pretty dramatic, but it's not interesting to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's perky, active, pretty, and very sensitive both mentally and physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really lucky to have someone like her as a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes she's too emotional and careless,\Nbut that also makes her attractive and pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But somehow I felt as if I wasn't getting enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mai Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, ever since I've met her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, even when I'm with with my Rie, I can't get the affair with her out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her eyes, her voice, her lips, her body, her hips, her tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that feeling when we were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pleasure each time I came...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why can't I forget her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been happy with Rie until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now, even one month after our affair...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since then I haven't done it with her, and it was only a one time fling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more time. Just once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The training program must be boring to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No it isn't, but I want to work in the real office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll get the assignment you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I got my assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The editing division of Neo Economy Magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Neo Economy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was established later than its competitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but its market share has been expanding a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look down on me just because I'm an office assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a little about my company!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the editor in chief is a really sharp, beautiful woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...and all the female employees admire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be working under her, Ms. Sugiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the editor in chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the office is real competitive, but I'm confident I can hold my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I know you're good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sugiyama is very attractive, even to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, that's what you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she is attractive, she's such a conservative boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I have a girlfriend called Rie Saito already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, you're a lot more attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this sticky liquid soap or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hiroki Ono, assigned to work here starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,About your responsibilities, please consult with Mr. Fukuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rewrite it again, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, Professor Taylor from Yale University on line three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is she.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if she's an role model among female employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch, I'm going to surpass her one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking the time to call us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're studying pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at least to cover all the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very quick, and you've made no mistakes so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to read and it fits the article's space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find this in any magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good enough if you just copy from other material.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have a good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the main topic isn't focused, and it's not well organized over all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe readers will find it interesting at first, but nobody will want to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for a rookie, it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were another magazine it would be good enough, but not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look at it again, and rewrite it from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I get acclimated, it won't be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an appointment with Professor Yee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes .
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaiba, pass this on to the Administration Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Saba, tomorrow's interview with Professor Makuyama will be at 3 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be fine, in one month, I'll beat all those senior workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without a doubt, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You look depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you exhausted from just your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure working at Neo Economy must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal working there, and I'm not tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, raising your voice to me all of sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The work isn't that hard and it's really worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe you're thinking about Ms. Sugiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit, that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You look ready for some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be tired so this time, I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking back now, I was falling for Ms. Sugiyama from the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? The last one was much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I' m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've been so down for over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my mind, I was picturing how miserable I was without any idea what to do at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That image of myself was awful, and I was too wimpy to say anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And since I bragged so much, I couldn't even open up to Rie so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so alone, struggling all by myself, and that had me preoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't done it for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you bored with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have another girl besides me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You found out that you're gay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you don't like me anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much, so don't dump me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's getting harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was getting hard when I thought of Ms. Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt sorry for Rie, getting excited for me without knowing my secret fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I just couldn't say anything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I couldn't wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you come...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I should be home by the afternoon. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ono, it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost 9 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't study during work hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very enthusiastic, but don't work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, what about yourself at this late hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to play golf with some clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasted my day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way home, I saw the light in the office, so I stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are staying much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lock the door so you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
